{"tid":1293013,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"[I/A] 巨龍國度 Brave Conquest","createTime":"2019-07-07T14:17:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-18T04:40:21.000Z","uid":186,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"ccf1e0c3283f0d5f7cfc2e9b79d65897256c0643","tid":1293013,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T14:17:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://image.gameapps.hk/images/201907/02/COVER.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.gameapps.hk%2Fimages%2F201907%2F02%2FCOVER.jpg&h=f24a715d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【自由城建、領地經營】 <br />\n城鎮內各式各樣建築物隨你升級與建造，玩家可以自由擺放並努力滿足居民所提出的政務需求。內政訂單、海港貿易、開墾農田、建設工廠，隨心打造專屬國度，展現你獨特的領主風範！<br />\n<img src=\"https://image.gameapps.hk/images/201907/02/2de0fb299457bffb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.gameapps.hk%2Fimages%2F201907%2F02%2F2de0fb299457bffb.jpg&h=ad0e5e37&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【奇景探索、開疆辟土】 <br />\n遊戲搭配 3D 影像畫面呈現出細緻大世界，從平原、雪山、港灣、古墓等，再到神秘的埋骨之地，尋找各種失落奇觀，展開獨一無二的奇幻冒險旅程！ <br />\n<img src=\"https://image.gameapps.hk/images/201907/02/08b3deac7094f3c9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.gameapps.hk%2Fimages%2F201907%2F02%2F08b3deac7094f3c9.jpg&h=04b42b2e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【攻城略地、實時激戰】 <br />\n實時兵團戰鬥玩法，戰略方針決定成敗！自由佈置軍團，各獨特兵種配搭不同的英雄技能與法術施放。傳說中的冰、火、毒、狂暴、光盾、治療等各式古老法術，重現於戰場上，使實時兵團戰鬥更加緊張刺激！ <br />\n<img src=\"https://image.gameapps.hk/images/201907/02/44fff53cf8868a03.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.gameapps.hk%2Fimages%2F201907%2F02%2F44fff53cf8868a03.jpg&h=0b560137&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【英雄培養、兵團搭配】 <br />\n號召數十位各具特色的英雄，組成獨一無二的軍團陣容盡在您麾下。他們將在探索的旅程中與你相遇，籠絡他們加入你的陣營！多達 60 樣兵種與各善惡英雄組成獨特的兵團，強化你的國力，成為巨龍國度的締造者。 <br />\n<img src=\"https://image.gameapps.hk/images/201907/02/3f2953d83fea7487.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.gameapps.hk%2Fimages%2F201907%2F02%2F3f2953d83fea7487.jpg&h=9ba0a23e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【聯盟創建、強強連手】 <br />\n遊戲內資源不夠？聯盟魔法池為你提供龐大的資源。兵力不足？集合盟友一起並肩作戰，有福同享，有難同當，一同邁向王座之路。 <br />\n<img src=\"https://image.gameapps.hk/images/201907/02/987e33909a3082e4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.gameapps.hk%2Fimages%2F201907%2F02%2F987e33909a3082e4.jpg&h=7cce5197&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\niOS下載連結：<a href=\"https://apple.co/2Xl2meJ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapple.co%2F2Xl2meJ&d=P0gT%2F24t7mhr82HgIt0JldVSC25YwgVwXuaRRXYDXIw%3D&h=9572fa26\" target=\"_blank\">https://apple.co/2Xl2meJ</a><br />\nAndroid下載連結：<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2xqvhTY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2xqvhTY&d=P0gT%2F24t7mhr82HgIt0JldVSC25YwgVwXuaRRXYDXIw%3D&h=a0ec0e9f\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2xqvhTY</a>"},{"pid":"e704ed073cdf0a04d9b47ae646210a8665ee4dcf","tid":1293013,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T14:17:44.000Z","msg":"新開Game"},{"pid":"ef5db41871d07d4675f07a2c10fd8a3263073414","tid":1293013,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T14:18:08.000Z","msg":"有得控兵 升城"},{"pid":"b797d5c0e9a53ce8a80d1cd75b9b0e7928311212","tid":1293013,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T14:18:41.000Z","msg":"唔駛首抽"},{"pid":"5c5256257c5bfc83f12dad21205fdca1f6f968f4","tid":1293013,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T14:19:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c73b1e958cbcf368ba2e60e1a4a295c3e65cc584","tid":1293013,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T14:21:33.000Z","msg":"畫風都幾得意"},{"pid":"f110e47e3589c98ef2c1edcf62a2456945d2e1ba","tid":1293013,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T14:21:46.000Z","msg":"未知洗唔洗重課"},{"pid":"a7082dcd66fab361db2deae12153933767fff41b","tid":1293013,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T14:23:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75ac5db437814c81d210417705822bf7315d0be4","tid":1293013,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T14:31:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bda0004df141c2e339c952bede045dad9a8c30cf","tid":1293013,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T14:50:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"838e676802129e7afedd89875b30fb74278cba00","tid":1293013,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T14:59:55.000Z","msg":"盡量整合俾現場手足<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">-唔好即刻坐紅巴(重要)<br />\n-建議行遠少少再上巴士/其他地鐵站(重要)<br />\n-山東街，彌敦道，朗豪坊都全部防暴，意味著三邊圍攻<br />\n-波鞋街有狗車full gear 兜入去<br />\n-地鐵站一定有狗，自己小心(好似閂曬) CONFIRM唔到SORRY<br />\n-朗豪坊正門，後門已鎖，旁邊側門未鎖<br />\n-麥花臣球場出面幾架警車<br />\n-佐敦交界彌敦道警犬佈防玩四面圍<br />\n-可以考慮入商店購物/去食野(重要)<br />\n-維景去樂富103 <br />\n-行遠少少搭巴士一定最安全<br />\n-唔好自己落單，除非搵到機會混入人群（一定俾狗抄牌）</span>"},{"pid":"53bd01ee71423fcf3641f66a95f93b1121dc1b1c","tid":1293013,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T15:00:07.000Z","msg":"香港人 加油"},{"pid":"ed98afef965aea9ca0c2ff8d6ffc7deef2b34ae9","tid":1293013,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T17:07:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0ec76d2d3c41656eff4035d6f34efc7554437b7","tid":1293013,"uid":141263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T15:04:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/HjSdIcYznuk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com